{"tid":834282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台男大生BBQ幾乎變盲 元兇竟是錫紙烤花甲","createTime":"2018-09-24T05:52:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T06:31:26.000Z","uid":49974,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e0935cc7c64e210b2742b8caa7d1ef94c97e2c16","tid":834282,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T05:52:31.000Z","msg":"中秋節是約三五知己燒烤的好時機，不過台灣一名男大學生日前和朋友燒烤狂歡時，原本只想確認燒烤架上的花甲是否熟透，不料當他靠近打開錫紙時，卻因距離太近，錫紙內的高溫蒸氣噴出，令其雙眼慘被灼傷，幾乎無法睜開，立即到醫院求診。<br />\n<br />\n據台媒報道，台北慈濟醫院眼科主治醫生表示，早前接獲該名20多歲男大生雙眼被灼傷的個案，詢問後始知他在燒烤時受傷，雙眼被熱氣熏得無法睜開，雙眼角膜也變得白濛濛一片。<br />\n<br />\n醫生解釋，蛋白質經高溫烹煮都會變成固體白色，人的眼球亦是一樣，因角膜細胞含有蛋白質，遇熱會變白，幸而傷者只是表皮受損，未會致盲，經治療兩星期後，視力已經逐漸復原。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20180924/bkn-20180924011336562-0924_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20180924%2Fbkn-20180924011336562-0924_00952_001.html&d=TdIywUwWg4I4fsrcBNr70E%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=2e34e639\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20180924/bkn-20180924011336562-0924_00952_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n一定好撚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2b14606cbba325ce40d01205d8da8d4a1d80570","tid":834282,"uid":24180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T06:01:56.000Z","msg":"佢隊個頭埋去開??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e235ab4982fbde9efe2974b9c1097fde2b2c9519","tid":834282,"uid":59830,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T06:09:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e748d8310ab4947b1d9044e88889c6e1ce7c140","tid":834282,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T06:16:45.000Z","msg":"佢究境隊到幾埋先會咁"},{"pid":"b2d68c6184dca122c5ece3ea512c6791fedc75a2","tid":834282,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit